The model was trained using the Adam optimizer and the cross-entropy loss function. To address the class imbalance issue and improve the performance of the model across different classes, a learnable class weight vector wc is introduced into the loss function, which is defined as follows:7\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
